      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，先commit一个初始版本到main。然后branch newbranch切出去，checkout到newbranch上做开发，再commit一次。之后切回main继续推进，最后把newbranch合并进来。",
      "elements_involved": [
